reviewText: My family and I greatly enjoyed this movie. My eight year old son loved it so much that we took it out of the Library twice. Now, I'm considering buying it so we can watch it whenever we like... . Recommended for children and adults.
Great story about Leonardo, good for middle school children.
This video is not as good as other videos in this series.  My older kids like it, but the younger ones find it a little boring.
